'''-{zh:氰化物;zh-hans:氰化物;zh-hant:氰化物;zh-hk:山埃;zh-tw:氰化物;zh-mo:山埃;}-'''（{{lang-en|Cyanide}}）是特指带有[[氰|氰]]离子（CN<sup>−</sup>）或氰基（-CN）的化合物，其中的[[碳|碳]][[原子|原子]]和[[氮|氮]]原子通过叁键相连接。<ref>[[IUPAC_Gold_Book|IUPAC Gold Book]] [http://goldbook.iupac.org/C01486.html ''cyanides''] {{Wayback|url=http://goldbook.iupac.org/C01486.html |date=20170107225157 }}</ref>

[[无机化合物|无机]]氰化物俗稱'''山奈'''或'''山埃'''（來自[[英語|英語]]音譯），是指包含有氰根离子（CN<sup>−</sup>）的无机盐，可认为是[[氢氰酸|氢氰酸]]（HCN）的盐。可溶的氰化物如：[[氰化钾|氰化钾]]和[[氰化钠|氰化钠]]有剧毒。<ref name="CMC">{{Cite web| url=http://www.cyanidecode.org/cyanide_environmental.php| title=Environmental and Health Effects of Cyanide| publisher=International Cyanide Management Institute| year=2006| access-date=4 August 2009| archive-date=2012-11-30| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121130094124/http://www.cyanidecode.org/cyanide_environmental.php| dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[氢氰酸|氢氰酸]]，又叫氰化氢，化学式 HCN，是一种[[挥发性|挥发性]]高的液体，在工业上大量生产。它可由氰化物酸化而成。

另有[[有机化合物|有机]]氰化物，是由氰基通过[[单键|单键]]与另外的碳原子结合而成，通常叫做[[腈|腈]]。举个例子，[[乙腈|乙腈]]是由氰基和[[甲基|甲基]] (CH<sub>3</sub>)键合而成的化合物。尽管它们通常不释放氰离子，但[[羟腈|羟腈]]会这样做，所以有毒。

氰化物在英文中称为cyanide，由cyan（[[青色|青色]]，蓝绿色）衍生而来。考虑单质的氰[(CN)<sub>2</sub>]呈[[气态|气态]]，故以青字加上气字头，得到现在通行的氰字。而英文中将氰与青色相联系，是因为当時发现的著名的[[普鲁士蓝|普鲁士蓝]]是一种蓝色的[[染料|染料]]，为含氰无机物。

==成键==
氰离子和[[氮气|氮气]]、[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]是[[等电子体|等电子体]]。在碳和氮原子之间有一个三键。氰离子的负电荷聚集在碳原子上。<ref>Greenwood, N. N.; & Earnshaw, A. (1997). Chemistry of the Elements (2nd Edn.), Oxford:Butterworth-Heinemann. {{ISBN|0-7506-3365-4}}.</ref><ref>G. L. Miessler and D. A. Tarr "Inorganic Chemistry" 3rd Ed, Pearson/Prentice Hall publisher, {{ISBN|0-13-035471-6}}.</ref>

== 存在 ==
===自然界===
[[File:Removal_of_cyanide_poison_from_cassava.jpg|thumb]]的[[木薯|木薯]]中去除氰化物。]]
氰化物可以由某些[[细菌|细菌]]、[[真菌|真菌]]和[[藻类|藻类]]生产。它是许多植物的拒食剂。在某些种子和果核中可发现相当量的氰化物，例如[[苦杏仁|苦杏仁]]、[[杏|杏]]、[[苹果|苹果]]和[[桃|桃]]的种子和果核。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.atsdr.cdc.gov/toxfaqs/tf.asp?id=71&tid=19 |title=ToxFAQs for Cyanide |access-date=2008-06-28 |date=July 2006 |publisher=[[Agency_for_Toxic_Substances_and_Disease_Registry|Agency for Toxic Substances and Disease Registry]] |archive-date=2019-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190614144336/https://www.atsdr.cdc.gov/toxfaqs/tf.asp?id=71&tid=19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>可以释放氰化物的化合物称为氰基化合物。在植物中，氰化物通常和[[糖|糖]]分子键合，形成氰[[苷|苷]]，抵御[[草食动物|草食动物]]。[[木薯|木薯]]根是热带国家种植的一种重要的，类似[[马铃薯|马铃薯]]的食物（也是制作{{le|tapioca}}的原材料）也含有氰苷。<ref>{{Cite journal|first=J. |last=Vetter |title=Plant cyanogenic glycosides |journal=Toxicon |year=2000 |volume=38 |pages=11–36 |doi=10.1016/S0041-0101(99)00128-2 |pmid=10669009 |issue=1}}</ref><ref name=jones>{{Cite journal|first=D. A. |last=Jones |title= Why are so many food plants cyanogenic? |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_phytochemistry_1998-01_47_2/page/155 |journal=[[Phytochemistry_(journal)|Phytochemistry]] |year=1998 |volume=47 |pages=155–162 |doi=10.1016/S0031-9422(97)00425-1 |pmid=9431670 |issue=2}}</ref>

===介质===
{{le|氰基自由基|cyanide radical}} ·CN 存在于[[星际介质|星际介质]]中。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Pieniazek |first=Piotr A. |author2=Bradforth, Stephen E. |author3=Krylov, Anna I. |title=Spectroscopy of the Cyano Radical in an Aqueous Environment |date=2005-12-07 |pages=4854–65 |issue=14 |volume=110 |url=http://www-bcf.usc.edu/~krylov/pubs/pdf/jpca-110-4854.pdf |journal=The Journal of Physical Chemistry A |pmid=16599455 |doi=10.1021/jp0545952 |bibcode=2006JPCA..110.4854P |access-date=2008-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080911131555/http://www-bcf.usc.edu/~krylov/pubs/pdf/jpca-110-4854.pdf |archive-date=2008-09-11 |url-status=dead }}</ref> [[氰气|氰气]] (CN)<sub>2</sub>可用来测量[[分子云|分子云]]的温度。<ref>{{cite journal |title = Interstellar Cyanogen and the Temperature of the Cosmic Microwave Background Radiation |author1 = Roth, K. C. |author2 = Meyer, D. M. |author3 = Hawkins, I. |journal = The Astrophysical Journal |year = 1993 |volume = 413 |issue = 2 |pages = L67–L71 |doi = 10.1086/186961 |bibcode = 1993ApJ...413L..67R |url = http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1993ApJ...413L..67R&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf |access-date = 2022-01-05 |archive-date = 2021-08-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210816092223/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1993ApJ...413L..67R&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>

===热分解和燃烧产物===
氢氰酸可以由某些材料在缺氧环境下的[[热分解|热分解]]而成。举个例子，它可以在[[内燃机|内燃机]][[尾气|尾气]]和[[烟草|烟草]]烟雾中被检测到。某些[[塑料|塑料]]，特别是[[丙烯腈|丙烯腈]]的衍生物加热或燃烧会产生氢氰酸。<ref name="CDC"/>

===辅因子===
[[氢化酶|氢化酶]]的活性位点含有与铁相连的氰根[[配体|配体]]。[NiFe]-氢化酶的氰化物生物合成来自[[氨甲酰磷酸酯|氨甲酰磷酸酯]]，它会被转化成[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]][[硫氰酸酯|硫氰酸酯]]，一种CN<sup>−</sup> 供体。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Reissmann |first1=Stefanie |last2=Hochleitner |first2=Elisabeth |last3=Wang |first3=Haofan |last4=Paschos |first4=Athanasios |last5=Lottspeich |first5=Friedrich |last6=Glass |first6=Richard S. |last7=Böck |first7=August |title=Taming of a Poison: Biosynthesis of the NiFe-Hydrogenase Cyanide Ligands |journal=Science |volume=299 |issue=5609 |pages=1067–70 |year=2003 |pmid=12586941 |doi=10.1126/science.1080972 |bibcode=2003Sci...299.1067R |s2cid=20488694 |url=http://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/d359/5a5928df6c6209f88e105c937ccce0a05237.pdf }}</ref>

==反应==
===水解===
氰化物在水中不稳定，但反应在170 °C之前都很缓慢。它的[[水解|水解]]会产生毒性远低于氰化物的[[氨|氨]]和[[甲酸盐|甲酸盐]]：<ref name=Ullmann/>
:CN<sup>-</sup>  +  2{{nbsp}}H<sub>2</sub>O  →  HCO<sub>2</sub><sup>-</sup>  +  NH<sub>3</sub>

===烷基化===
氰离子有高[[亲核性|亲核性]]，所以氰基很容易引入到有机化合物中，并替换掉一个[[卤素|卤素]]原子（例如[[氯甲烷|氯甲烷]]的[[氯|氯]]原子）。有机氰化物被称为腈。在有机合成中，氰化物是C-1 [[合成子|合成子]]，可以使碳链的长度加一：<ref>{{Ullmann|doi=10.1002/14356007.a17_363|title=Nitriles|year=2000|last1=Pollak|first1=Peter|last2=Romeder|first2=Gérard|last3=Hagedorn|first3=Ferdinand|last4=Gelbke|first4=Heinz-Peter|isbn=3527306730}}</ref>
:RX + CN<sup>−</sup> → RCN + X<sup>−</sup> 

===氧化还原反应===
氰离子是[[还原剂|还原剂]]，会被强[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]如[[氯气|氯气]] (Cl<sub>2</sub>)、[[次氯酸盐|次氯酸盐]] (ClO<sup>−</sup>)和[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]] (H<sub>2</sub>O<sub>2</sub>)[[氧化|氧化]]。这些氧化剂在[[金矿开采|金矿开采]]中用于消除含氰废水。<ref name="Young_1995">Young, C. A., & Jordan, T. S. (1995, May). Cyanide remediation: current and past technologies. In: Proceedings of the 10th Annual Conference on Hazardous Waste Research (pp. 104-129). Kansas State University: Manhattan, KS. https://engg.ksu.edu/HSRC/95Proceed/young.pdf {{Wayback|url=https://engg.ksu.edu/HSRC/95Proceed/young.pdf |date=20210706225524 }}</ref><ref name="SRK">{{Cite web |title=Cyanide Destruction {{!}} SRK Consulting |author=Dmitry Yermakov |work=srk.com |date= |access-date=2 March 2021 |url=https://www.srk.com/en/publications/cyanide-destruction# |language=en |archive-date=2021-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117202031/https://www.srk.com/en/publications/cyanide-destruction |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Botz">Botz Michael M. Overview of cyanide treatment methods. Elbow Creek Engineering, Inc. http://www.botz.com/MEMCyanideTreatment.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://www.botz.com/MEMCyanideTreatment.pdf |date=20210706225521 }}</ref>

===配合===
氰离子会和[[过渡金属|过渡金属]]反应，形成{{le|氰配合物|Cyanometalate|M-CN键}}。这个反应也是氰化物的毒性来源。<ref>Sharpe, A. G. The Chemistry of Cyano Complexes of the Transition Metals; Academic Press: London, 1976</ref>金属对这种[[阴离子|阴离子]] 高亲和力可归因于其负电荷、致密性和参与π键合的能力。

最重要的氰配合物是[[铁氰酸钾|铁氰酸钾]]和染料[[普鲁士蓝|普鲁士蓝]]。由于氰离子和铁原子紧密成键，它们都没有毒。<ref name=Holl>{{ cite book |author1=Holleman, A. F. |author2=Wiberg, E. | title = Inorganic Chemistry | publisher = Academic Press | location = San Diego | year = 2001 | isbn = 978-0-12-352651-9 }}</ref> 

==制备==
{{main|氰化氢#制取}}
在[[安德鲁索夫氧化反应|安德鲁索夫氧化反应]]中，[[氢氰酸|氢氰酸]]是由[[甲烷|甲烷]]和[[氨|氨]]在[[氧气|氧气]]和[[铂|铂]][[催化剂|催化剂]]存在下反应而成的。<ref>{{cite journal
 |title=Über die schnell verlaufenden katalytischen Prozesse in strömenden Gasen und die Ammoniak-Oxydation (V) |trans-title=About the quicka catalytic processes in flowing gases and the ammonia oxidation (V) |language=de |author-link1=Leonid Andrussow |first1=Leonid |last1=Andrussow |journal=Berichte der Deutschen Chemischen Gesellschaft |volume=60 |issue=8 |pages=2005–18 |year=1927 |doi=10.1002/cber.19270600857 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Über die katalytische Oxydation von Ammoniak-Methan-Gemischen zu Blausäure |trans-title=About the catalytic oxidation of ammonia-methane mixtures to cyanide |language=de |first1=L. |last1=Andrussow |journal=[[Angewandte_Chemie|Angewandte Chemie]] |volume=48 |issue=37 |pages=593–5 |year=1935 |doi=10.1002/ange.19350483702 }}</ref>
:2 CH<sub>4</sub> + 2 NH<sub>3</sub> + 3 O<sub>2</sub> → 2 HCN + 6 H<sub>2</sub>O

氰化钠是很多氰化物的前体，可以由[[氢氰酸|氢氰酸]]和[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]反应而成：<ref name=Ullmann />
:HCN  +  NaOH   →   NaCN  +  H<sub>2</sub>O

== 毒性 ==
{{main|氰化物中毒}}
很多氰化物都是剧毒的。氰离子是一种[[细胞色素c氧化酶|细胞色素c氧化酶]]（又称aa<sub>3</sub>）的[[酶抑制剂|酶抑制剂]]，这是在[[真核细胞|真核细胞]]的[[线粒体内膜|线粒体内膜]]中发现的第四种[[电子传递链|电子传递链]]配合物。氰离子附着在这种蛋白质中的铁原子上。氰化物与这种酶的结合阻止了电子从[[细胞色素c氧化酶|细胞色素c氧化酶]]到氧气的传输。结果，电子传递链被破坏，细胞不能再有氧地产生[[三磷酸腺苷|ATP]]来获取能量了。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Nelson|first1=David L.|last2=Cox|first2=Michael M.|title=Lehniger Principles of Biochemistry|publisher=[[Worth_Publishers|Worth Publishers]]|year=2000|location=New York|edition=3rd|isbn=978-1-57259-153-0|pages=[https://archive.org/details/lehningerprincip01lehn/page/668 668,670–71,676]|url=https://archive.org/details/lehningerprincip01lehn/page/668}}</ref>高度依赖[[有氧呼吸|有氧呼吸]]的组织，例如[[中枢神经系统|中枢神经系统]]和[[心脏|心脏]]受到的影响最大。这是{{le|组织毒性缺氧|Histotoxic hypoxia}}的例子。<ref name=Biller>{{cite book
|title=Interface of neurology and internal medicine
|edition=illustrated
|first1=José
|last1=Biller
|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins
|year=2007
|isbn=978-0-7817-7906-7
|page=939
|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SRIvmTVcYBwC
|access-date=2021-08-17
|archive-date=2020-03-18
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318053433/https://books.google.com/books?id=SRIvmTVcYBwC
|dead-url=no
}}, [https://books.google.com/books?id=SRIvmTVcYBwC&pg=PA939 Chapter 163, page 939] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SRIvmTVcYBwC&pg=PA939 |date=20200316014246 }}</ref>

最危险的氰化物是[[氢氰酸|氢氰酸]]，它是一种气体，可以通过吸入杀人。因此，在使用氢氰酸工作时，必须佩戴由外部氧气源供应的呼吸器。<ref name="CDC">{{Cite web|url=https://emergency.cdc.gov/agent/cyanide/basics/facts.asp|title=Facts about cyanide:Where cyanide is found and how it is used|last=Anon|date=June 27, 2013|work=CDC Emergency preparedness and response|publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|access-date=10 December 2016|archive-date=2019-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003012433/https://emergency.cdc.gov/agent/cyanide/basics/facts.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>氢氰酸可以由氰化物溶液和酸反应而成。氰化物的碱性溶液相对安全，因为它们不会放出氰化氢气体。氢氰酸也可以由[[聚氨酯|聚氨酯]]的燃烧产生，因此不建议将聚氨酯用于家用和飞机家具。口服低至 200 毫克的氰化物溶液，或暴露于270 [[ppm|ppm]] 氰化物的空气中，足以在几分钟内导致死亡。<ref name=Biller/>

[[腈|腈]]不准备放出氰离子，所以毒性较低。作为对比，像是[[三甲基氰硅烷|三甲基氰硅烷]] (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>SiCN的化合物遇水放出HCN 或氰离子。<ref>{{cite web |title=Cyanide |url=https://www.chemeurope.com/en/encyclopedia/Cyanide.html |website=Chemeurope.com |access-date=11 July 2019 |archive-date=2019-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711084748/https://www.chemeurope.com/en/encyclopedia/Cyanide.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 解毒 ===
[[羟钴胺|羟钴胺]]会和氰化物反应，形成可以安全被肾脏清除的[[氰钴胺|氰钴胺]]。这种方法的优点是避免形成高铁血红蛋白（见下文）。该解毒剂试剂盒以品牌Cyanokit销售，并于2006年获得美国食品药品监督管理局的批准。<ref>{{EMedicine|article|814287|Cyanide Toxicity|treatment}}</ref>

一个较旧的氰化物解毒剂试剂盒包括三种物质的给药：[[亚硝酸异戊酯|亚硝酸异戊酯]]（通过吸入给药）、[[亚硝酸钠|亚硝酸钠]]和[[硫代硫酸钠|硫代硫酸钠]]。解毒剂的目标是产生大量的[[三价铁|三价铁]] (Fe<sup>3+</sup>)，以便和细胞色素 a<sub>3</sub> 竞争氰化物（这样氰化物将与解毒剂，而不是酶结合）。[[亚硝酸盐|亚硝酸盐]]会把[[血红蛋白|血红蛋白]][[氧化|氧化]]成[[高铁血红蛋白|高铁血红蛋白]]，它与细胞色素氧化酶竞争氰离子。这形成高铁血红蛋白，并恢复[[细胞色素c氧化酶|细胞色素c氧化酶]]。它们从体内去除氰化物的主要机制是通过[[线粒体|线粒体]]酶{{le|硫氰酸盐酶|Rhodanese}}促转化为[[硫氰酸盐|硫氰酸盐]]。硫氰酸盐是一种相对无毒的分子，由肾脏排泄。为了加速这种解毒，人们使用硫代硫酸钠来为{{le|硫氰酸盐酶|Rhodanese}}提供硫，这是生产硫氰酸盐所必需的。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Chaudhary | first1 = M. | last2 = Gupta | first2 = R. | year = 2012 | title = Cyanide Detoxifying Enzyme: Rhodanese | journal = Current Biotechnology | volume = 1 | issue = 4 | pages = 327–335 | doi = 10.2174/2211550111201040327 }}</ref>

==应用==
=== 采矿业 ===
{{main|黃金氰化法}}
氰化物被大量用于[[黄金|黄金]]和[[银|银]]的开采中，它有助于溶解这些金属，从而与其他固体分离。在[[黄金氰化法|黄金氰化法]]中，将精细研磨的高品位矿石与氰化物混合（NaCN与矿石的比例约为 1:500）；低品位矿石则被堆成一堆，然后喷上氰化物溶液（NaCN与矿石的比例约为 1:1000）。这些贵金属和氰[[阴离子|阴离子]]配合，形成可溶的 [Au(CN)<sub>2</sub>]<sup>−</sup> 和[Ag(CN)<sub>2</sub>]<sup>−</sup>。<ref name=Ullmann>{{Ullmann |first1=Andreas |last1=Rubo |first2=Raf |last2=Kellens |first3=Jay |last3=Reddy |first4=Norbert |last4=Steier |first5=Wolfgang |last5=Hasenpusch |title=Alkali Metal Cyanides |year=2006 |doi=10.1002/14356007.i01_i01}}</ref>

::4 Au + 8 NaCN + O<sub>2</sub> + 2 H<sub>2</sub>O → 4 Na[Au(CN)<sub>2</sub>] + 4 NaOH
::Ag<sub>2</sub>S + 4 NaCN + H<sub>2</sub>O → 2 Na[Ag(CN)<sub>2</sub>] + NaSH + NaOH

===医药用途===
一种氰化物——[[硝普钠|硝普钠]]主要用于[[临床化学|临床化学]]测量[[尿|尿]]的[[酮体|酮体]]，主要作为[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]患者的追蹤。它有时用于紧急医疗情况下，使人类的[[血压|血压]]迅速下降；它还用作血管研究中的[[血管扩张剂|血管扩张剂]]。[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]期间，[[日本|日本]]医生曾短暂使用铜氰化物治疗[[肺结核|肺结核]]和[[麻风病|麻风病]]。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Takano |first=R. |date=August 1916 |title=The treatment of leprosy with cyanocuprol |journal=The Journal of Experimental Medicine |volume=24 |issue=2 |pages=207–211 |url=http://www.jem.org/cgi/content/abstract/24/2/207 |access-date=2008-06-28 |doi=10.1084/jem.24.2.207 |pmc=2125457 |pmid=19868035 |archive-date=2005-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050327015043/http://www.jem.org/cgi/content/abstract/24/2/207 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===非法捕鱼和偷猎===
{{Main|{{le|氰化物钓鱼|Cyanide fishing}}}}
氰化物被非法用于在[[珊瑚礁|珊瑚礁]]附近为[[水族馆|水族馆]]和海鲜市场捕获活鱼。这种做法具有争议性、危险性和破坏性，但受到利润丰厚的外来鱼类市场的推动。<ref name="crc">Dzombak, David A; Ghosh, Rajat S; Wong-Chong, George M. ''Cyanide in Water and Soil''. [[CRC_Press|CRC Press]], 2006, Chapter 11.2: "Use of Cyanide for Capturing Live Reef Fish".</ref>

非洲的偷猎者使用氰化物来把水坑弄毒，杀死大象以获取象牙。<ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-09-25/zimbabwe-poachers-kill-80-elephants-with-cyanide/4981372 Poachers kill 80 elephants with cyanide in Zimbabwe] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-09-25/zimbabwe-poachers-kill-80-elephants-with-cyanide/4981372 |date=20211213092354 }} ''ABC News'', 25 September 2013. Retrieved 30 October 2015.</ref>

===除害虫===
{{le|M44氰化物设备|M44 (cyanide device)}}在美国被用来杀死[[土狼|土狼]]和其他犬科动物。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1002/wsb.361|title=Animal attendance at M-44 sodium cyanide ejector sites for coyotes|journal=Wildlife Society Bulletin|volume=38|pages=217–220|year=2014|last1=Shivik|first1=John A.|last2=Mastro|first2=Lauren|last3=Young|first3=Julie K.|url=http://digitalcommons.unl.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=2419&context=icwdm_usdanwrc|access-date=2021-08-17|archive-date=2018-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719025200/https://digitalcommons.unl.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=2419&context=icwdm_usdanwrc|dead-url=no}}</ref>氰化物还用于[[新西兰|新西兰]]的动物控制，特别是[[刷尾负鼠|刷尾负鼠]]。这是一种外来引入的有袋动物，威胁到本地物种，并在牛群中传播[[结核病|结核病]]。氰化物也用于杀死本地鸟类，包括濒临灭绝的[[奇异鸟|奇异鸟]]。<ref>{{cite web |last = Green |first = Wren |title = The use of 1080 for pest control |publisher = New Zealand Department of Conservation |date = July 2004 |url = http://www.doc.govt.nz/upload/documents/conservation/threats-and-impacts/animal-pests/use-of-1080-04.pdf |access-date = 8 June 2011 |archive-date = 2012-10-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121004181826/http://www.doc.govt.nz/upload/documents/conservation/threats-and-impacts/animal-pests/use-of-1080-04.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>氰化物也可有效控制[[尤金袋鼠|尤金袋鼠]]，这是另一种引入新西兰的有袋动物害虫。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Shapiro|first=Lee|date=21 March 2011|title=Effectiveness of cyanide pellets for control of dama wallabies (Macropus eugenii)|journal=New Zealand Journal of Ecology |volume=35 |issue=3 |url=http://newzealandecology.org/nzje/new_issues/NZJEcol35_3_287.pdf |display-authors=etal}}</ref>在新西兰储存、处理和使用氰化物需要许可证。

氰化物被用作熏蒸船舶的[[杀虫剂|杀虫剂]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Sodium Cyanide|url=https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/sodium_cyanide|website=PubChem|publisher=National Center for Biotechnology Information|access-date=2 September 2016|date=2016|quote=Cyanide and hydrogen cyanide are used in electroplating, metallurgy, organic chemicals production, photographic developing, manufacture of plastics, fumigation of ships, and some mining processes.|archive-date=2021-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117205323/https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/sodium_cyanide|dead-url=no}}</ref>氰化物可用于杀死蚂蚁、<ref name="EPAReg1994">{{cite web|title=Reregistration Eligibility Decision (RED) Sodium Cyanide|url=https://archive.epa.gov/pesticides/reregistration/web/pdf/3086.pdf|website=EPA.gov|access-date=2 September 2016|page=7|date=1 September 1994|quote=Sodium cyanide was initially registered as a pesticide on December 23, 1947, to control ants on uncultivated agricultural and non-agricultural areas.|archive-date=2021-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210817101800/https://archive.epa.gov/pesticides/reregistration/web/pdf/3086.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>并在某些地方被用作老鼠药<ref name="TariffInfo1921">{{cite web|title=Tariff Information, 1921: Hearings on General Tariff Revision Before the Committee on Ways and Means, House of Representatives|url=http://www.abebooks.com/servlet/SearchResults?tn=Tariff+Information,+1921|website=AbeBooks.com|publisher=US Congress, House Committee on Ways and Means, US Government Printing Office|access-date=2 September 2016|page=3987|date=1921|quote=Another field in which cyanide is used in growing quantity is the eradication of rats and other vermin--especially in the fight against typhus.|archive-date=2021-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117202339/https://www.abebooks.com/servlet/SearchResults?tn=Tariff+Information%2C+1921|dead-url=no}}</ref>（现在毒性较低的[[砷|砷]]更常见）。<ref name="PlanetDeadly2013">{{cite web|title=Deadliest Poisons Used by Man|url=http://www.planetdeadly.com/human/deadliest-poisons-man|website=PlanetDeadly.com|access-date=2 September 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160511033535/http://www.planetdeadly.com/human/deadliest-poisons-man|archive-date=11 May 2016|date=18 November 2013}}</ref>

===其它用途===
尽管其有毒，氰化物和氰醇可促进各种植物的发芽。<ref>{{Cite journal|doi=10.1104/pp.52.1.23 |last1=Taylorson |first1=R. |last2=Hendricks |year=1973 |first2=SB |title=Promotion of Seed Germination by Cyanide |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_plant-physiology_1973-07_52_1/page/23 |journal=Plant Physiol. |volume=52 |issue=1 |pages=23–27 |pmid=16658492 |pmc=366431}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Mullick |first1=P. |year=1967 |last2=Chatterji |first2=U. N. |title=Effect of sodium cyanide on germination of two leguminous seeds |journal=Plant Systematics and Evolution |volume=114 |pages=88–91|doi=10.1007/BF01373937|s2cid=2533762 }}</ref>

====毒药====
人类蓄意使人[[氰化物中毒|氰化物中毒]]在历史上多次发生。<ref>{{Cite book
|title=Medical Management of Chemical Casualties Handbook
|edition=4
|last1=Bernan
|publisher=Government Printing Off
|year=2008
|isbn=978-0-16-081320-7
|page=41
|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oiw2ZzsBvsoC
|access-date=2021-08-17
|archive-date=2021-11-17
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117202252/https://books.google.com/books?id=oiw2ZzsBvsoC
|dead-url=no
}}, [https://books.google.com/books?id=oiw2ZzsBvsoC&pg=PA41 Extract p. 41] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oiw2ZzsBvsoC&pg=PA41 |date=20211117202231 }}</ref>常见的氰化物如[[氰化钠|氰化钠]]不是挥发性的，但可溶于水，所以可以意外摄入，使人中毒。[[氢氰酸|氢氰酸]]是一种气体，使其更加危险，但它比空气轻，并迅速扩散到大气中，这使得它作为[[化学武器|化学武器]]是无效的。氢氰酸在密闭空间内的毒性更有效，例如[[毒气室|毒气室]]中。最重要的是，从[[齐克隆B|齐克隆B]]颗粒中释放的氢氰酸被广泛用于[[纳粹大屠杀|纳粹大屠杀]]的[[灭绝营|灭绝营]]。

====食物添加剂====
由于氰离子和[[铁|铁]]的配合物非常稳定，亚铁氰酸盐（[[亚铁氰酸钠|亚铁氰酸钠]] E535、[[亚铁氰酸钾|亚铁氰酸钾]] E536和亚铁氰酸钙 E538<ref>{{cite book
