|isbn=978-1-85573-475-3
|page=459
|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IrYfDEl7XPYC
|access-date=2021-08-17
|archive-date=2021-08-17
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210817101759/https://books.google.com/books?id=IrYfDEl7XPYC
|dead-url=no
}} [https://books.google.com/books?id=IrYfDEl7XPYC&pg=PA459 Extract of page 459] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IrYfDEl7XPYC&pg=PA459 |date=20210817101759 }}</ref>）在人体内不会分解成致死量的氰化物，并在食品工业中用作如[[食盐|食盐]]中的[[抗结块剂|抗结块剂]]。<ref>{{cite book
